Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and emotion recognition in spoken language.
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper involves audio processing and feature extraction from speech signals.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper proposes a deep learning framework for multimodal emotion recognition.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper involves the use of machine learning techniques for emotion recognition.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the fusion of text and audio modalities for emotion recognition.
